---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import logo from "../logo.png";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy | Hangout!">
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-neo-bg">

    <!-- Nav -->
    <nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 bg-neo-bg border-b-4 border-black px-4 py-3">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto flex justify-between items-center">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-1 font-black uppercase tracking-tighter text-2xl">
          <img src={logo.src} alt="Hangout!" class="w-20 h-auto object-contain" />
          Hangout!
        </a>
        <div class="hidden md:flex gap-6 items-center font-bold">
          <a href="/#how-it-works" class="uppercase text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:px-3 hover:py-1 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-black transition-all">How It Works</a>
          <a href="/#safety" class="uppercase text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:px-3 hover:py-1 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-black transition-all">Safety</a>
          <a href="/communities" class="uppercase text-sm tracking-wide hover:bg-black hover:text-white hover:px-3 hover:py-1 border-2 border-transparent hover:border-black transition-all">Communities</a>
          <a href="/" class="font-black uppercase text-sm border-4 border-black px-4 py-2 bg-white shadow-neo hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back Home</a>
        </div>
        <a href="/" class="md:hidden font-black uppercase text-sm border-4 border-black px-4 py-2 bg-white shadow-neo hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors">← Back</a>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <header class="relative overflow-hidden border-b-4 border-black bg-neo-bg">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.06) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 40px 40px;"></div>

      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 pt-16 pb-24 relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 items-center mb-6">
          <span class="bg-neo-secondary border-2 border-black px-3 py-1 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest -rotate-1 shadow-neo inline-block">📄 Legal</span>
          <span class="bg-black text-white border-2 border-black px-3 py-1 font-black text-xs uppercase tracking-widest rotate-1 shadow-neo inline-block">Last updated: March 2026</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-black leading-[0.9] uppercase tracking-tighter mb-4">
          Privacy Policy<br/>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold max-w-xl border-l-4 border-black pl-5 py-2 bg-white/50">
          This page explains how we handle your data while you are on the Hangout! waitlist in Singapore.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>
    <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-16">
      <section class="bg-white border-4 border-black p-6 md:p-8 shadow-neo space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-black uppercase tracking-tight">PRIVACY POLICY (WAITLIST EDITION)</h2>
          <p class="mt-1 font-bold text-sm text-black/60">Last Updated: March 2026</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm md:text-base font-bold leading-relaxed text-black/80">
          <div>
            <p class="font-black mb-1">1. WHAT WE TAKE</p>
            <p class="mb-1">When you join the waitlist, we collect:</p>
            <p class="mb-1">
              <span class="font-black">Your School Email:</span>
              To verify you’re actually a student at a local Poly, Uni, ITE, or JC.
            </p>
            <p>
              <span class="font-black">Your Interaction Data:</span>
              If you vote for your school or request a community, we track that to see where the hype is.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black mb-1">2. WHAT WE DO WITH IT</p>
            <p class="mb-1">
              <span class="font-black">Verification:</span>
                We use your school email to confirm you’re a student. We also use this email to send you updates about the app launch.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black mb-1">3. WHAT WE DON'T DO</p>
            <p class="mb-1">We don’t sell your data. Not to advertisers, not to schools, not to parents.</p>
            <p class="mb-1">We only email you about the app launch and major community updates.</p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black mb-1">4. YOUR RIGHTS</p>
            <p>
              If you want off the list, email us at
              <a href="mailto:support@hangout.sg" class="underline underline-offset-2 decoration-black/60 hover:decoration-black">support@hangout.sg</a>.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div>
            <p class="font-black mb-1">5. UPDATES</p>
            <p>As we move from the waitlist to the App Store, this policy will evolve. We’ll notify you when the policy updates.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

      <footer class="bg-black text-neo-bg py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 mb-12">
        <div class="md:col-span-2">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-4">
            <img src={logo.src} alt="Hangout!" class="w-16 h-auto filter invert" />
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-black uppercase">Hangout!</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-bold text-white/70 max-w-md mb-6">
            Singapore's safe, verified student community platform. Built for students, by students.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-2 flex-wrap">
            <span class="bg-neo-secondary border-2 border-white/20 text-black px-2 py-1 font-black text-xs uppercase">🇸🇬 Singapore</span>
            <span class="bg-neo-primary border-2 border-white/20 text-white px-2 py-1 font-black text-xs uppercase">Students Only</span>
            <span class="border-2 border-white/20 px-2 py-1 font-black text-xs uppercase">Beta 2025</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black uppercase mb-4 text-neo-secondary">Platform</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70 font-bold">
            <li><a href="/communities" class="hover:text-neo-primary transition-colors">Communities</a></li>
            <li><a href="#how-it-works" class="hover:text-neo-primary transition-colors">How It Works</a></li>
            <li><a href="#safety" class="hover:text-neo-primary transition-colors">Safety</a></li>
            <li><button class="open-waitlist hover:text-neo-secondary transition-colors text-left">Join Waitlist</button></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-black uppercase mb-4 text-neo-secondary">Legal</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-white/70 font-bold">
            <li><a href="/privacy-policy" class="hover:text-neo-primary transition-colors">Privacy Policy</a></li>
            <li><a href="#" class="hover:text-neo-primary transition-colors">Contact Support</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="border-t-4 border-white/20 pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-white/40 text-sm">© 2025 Hangout! All rights reserved.</p>
        <p class="font-bold text-white/40 text-sm">Made with 💛 for Singapore students</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </footer>
  </div>
</Layout>
